{"tid":901594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Stan Lee逝世】後悔賺得不夠狠　迪士尼買Marvel分唔到一毫","createTime":"2018-11-14T06:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T15:03:30.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7df03136b3c3a498dba2efef347b37703e3fec36","tid":901594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"史丹李（Stan Lee）創造了美國動漫宇宙，他生前也備受敬重，但史丹李並不認為自己是一個成功的生意人。他曾表示過自己應可「再貪一點」，讓自己變得更富有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTbJf7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTbJf7G.jpg&h=c8202644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n史丹李坐擁一眾超級英級的版權，想必收版稅可「收到手軟」，但事實上史丹李並沒有想像之中那麼有錢。有美國網站估計他只分得5000萬美元（約3.9億港元），及不上任何一套Marvel作品的票房。<br />\n<br />\n後悔賺得不夠「狠」<br />\n<br />\n事實上史丹李對此亦有自知自明，他2016年接受雜誌《The Hollywood Reporter》採訪時，曾對自己一生中多次的決策感到後悔。他說道：「我做生意很蠢，我應該更貪的。」<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼在2009年花40億美元（約312億港元）購買Mavel的招牌，但史丹李卻一毫子也領不到。<br />\n<br />\n他後悔的是1998年與Marvel簽署協定，協議中Marvel聲稱會根據他創造的角色，在發行作品時計算版稅給他，但在2002年史丹李控告Marvel沒有支付他足夠版稅。雙方最終達成和解，史丹李可以從Marvel電影賺取的票房中抽10%作為收入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERKZyUm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERKZyUm.jpg&h=5be52621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUc8sen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUc8sen.jpg&h=1c7f3950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb60d8b9e91f99086dfc7573d48d3c419dd088b3","tid":901594,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"5000萬美金都唔錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55402bdb14c6dfa7eb33e1f2522a6f9cb0aeeddf","tid":901594,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb60d8b9e91f99086dfc7573d48d3c419dd088b3","tid":901594,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"5000萬美金都唔錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"對你黎講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d21619837edc63ff51f7d81ac05e3af9274333","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0f8f7769e293fbddc368241e669d61ff42a20e7","tid":901594,"uid":66943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"79d21619837edc63ff51f7d81ac05e3af9274333","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"拍完九萬世喇大佬"},{"pid":"79120d46e8a95af154b7c0fbeee1c36941d4771e","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47b2568cb872026f9ec6035e6bd09a1b8b5ca17a","tid":901594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79120d46e8a95af154b7c0fbeee1c36941d4771e","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f8f7769e293fbddc368241e669d61ff42a20e7","tid":901594,"uid":66943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"79d21619837edc63ff51f7d81ac05e3af9274333","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"拍完九萬世喇大佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"CG啦 paul walker都係咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed62e7008646828fd826f06bb931d2f9b8c21f0","tid":901594,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a505200c01af1364fdc3f93298f03c2895db2df9","tid":901594,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47b2568cb872026f9ec6035e6bd09a1b8b5ca17a","tid":901594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"